B

Base62 - Class in net.wenheqi.util.encoding
This class consists of static methods for obtaining encoders and decoders for the Base62 encoding scheme.
Base62.Decoder - Class in net.wenheqi.util.encoding
This class implements a decoder for decoding byte data using the Base62 encoding scheme as specified in Base62.Encoder.
Base62.Encoder - Class in net.wenheqi.util.encoding
This class implements an encoder for encoding data using the Base62 encoding scheme.

D

decode(byte[]) - Method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62.Decoder
Decodes all bytes from the input byte array using the Base62 encoding scheme, writing the results into a newly-allocated output byte array.
decode(String) - Method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62.Decoder
Converts each character in the str to a byte array of the corresponding index in alphabet, and then decode all bytes using the Base62 encoding scheme, writing the results into a newly-allocated output byte array.

E

encode(byte[]) - Method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62.Encoder
Encodes all bytes from the specified byte array into a newly-allocated byte array using the Base62 encoding scheme.
encode(int) - Method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62.Encoder
Converts the specified integer to a byte array and encodes all bytes from the specified number into a newly-allocated byte array using the Base62 encoding scheme.
encode(long) - Method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62.Encoder
Converts the specified long to a byte array and encodes all bytes from the specified number into a newly-allocated byte array using the Base62 encoding scheme.
encode(String) - Method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62.Encoder
Encodes this string into a sequence of bytes using StandardCharsets.UTF_8 and Encodes this byte array into a newly-allocated byte array using the Base62 encoding scheme.
encode(String, Charset) - Method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62.Encoder
Encodes this string into a sequence of bytes using the given charset and Encodes this byte array into a newly-allocated byte array using the Base62 encoding scheme.

G

getDecoder() - Static method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62
Returns a Base62.Decoder that decodes using the alphabet in Base62 Table.
getEncoder() - Static method in class net.wenheqi.util.encoding.Base62
Returns a Base62.Encoder that encodes using the alphabet in Base62 Table.
